title: The Music of Nashville (Original Soundtrack from Season 5), Vol. 1 - Nashville Cast
text: Formed: October 10, 2012 in Nashville, TN Genre: Country Years Active: '10s The Nashville Cast is just that, a loose configuration of actors, singers, and musicians who are part of the cast of the ABC television series Nashville, which had its debut on October 10, 2012. The series chronicles the lives of various fictional movers and shakers swept up in Nashville's music industry, and the songs they sing, write, sell, and share are a big part of the show's appeal. The various songs and performances, both covers and originals, are part of an ongoing release series handled... Top Albums and Songs by Nashville Cast 1.
